data.description: Charming 2 bed/2bath Webb City home!  This amazing home offers hardwood floors, an updated kitchen, built-ins, extra covered parking, and a large primary suite.  Inside, discover a spacious living room w/ fireplace that connects to a formal dining room and bright foyer.  The kitchen provides stainless appliances, Quartz counters, subway tile backsplash, and pantry storage.  Completing the main floor is a bedroom and full bathroom with washer/dryer connections.  Upstairs, enjoy a full floor primary suite w/ large walk-in closet, bathroom, and access to a sunroom.  Relax in the fully privacy fenced back yard with alley access to the 2 car carport and garage.  Quick access to Macarthur Drive.
